(61, 1, '2014-02-01 17:23:43', '2014-02-01 16:23:43', '<!--:SR-->Vlasnička struktura\r\n\r\nKompanija NIS Energowind doo je 2010. godine osnovala svoje zavisno društvo, kompaniju <b>Wind Park Plandište doo</b>, kao kompaniju koja će biti nosilac projekta izgradnje vetroelektrane „Plandište 1“ na teritoriji opštine Plandište. Planirano je da se ovaj projekat sastoji od 34 vetrogeneratora, ukupne instalisane snage 102 MW. 50% vlasništva kompanije je posredno u rukama kompanije NIS, a preostalih 50% je u vlasništvu privatnih investitora.\r\n<b>NIS</b> je jedna od najvećih vertikalno integrisanih kompanija u jugoistočnoj Evropi. Osnovne delatnosti su istraživanja, proizvodnja i prerada nafte i gasa, promet naftnih derivata, kao i realizacija projekata u oblasti petrohemije i energetike. Gazprom Neft poseduje 56,15% akcijskog kapitala NIS-a, dok je 29,88% akcija NIS-a u vlasništvu Republike Srbije. Ostatak pripada građanima, zaposlenima, bivšim zaposlenima i drugim manjinskim akcionarima.<!--:--><!--:en--><div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h1>Ownership structure</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h5>In 2010 NIS Energowind doo founded its subsidiary company, <b>Wind Park Plandište doo</b>, as leader of the project of construction of “Plandište 1“ wind park on the territory of the municipality Plandište. This project is planned to include 34 wind turbines, total installed power of 102 MW. Fifty percent of the Company ownership is indirectly held by NIS company, and the remaining 50% is owned by private investors.</h5>\r\n<b>NIS</b> is one of the largest vertically integrated companies in Southeast Europe. The core activities are research, production and processing of oil and gas, trade in oil derivatives as well as execution of projects in the field of petrochemistry and energy. Gazprom Neft holds 56.15% of NIS share capital, whereas 29.88% of NIS shares is held by the Republic of Serbia. The rest belongs to the citizens, employees, former employees and other minority shareholders.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div><!--:-->', '<!--:en-->Ownership structure<!--:--><!--:SR-->Vlasnička struktura<!--:-->', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-02-01 17:23:43', '2014-02-01 16:23:43', '', 15, 'http://nemanja-pc/?p=61', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
