(77, 1, '2014-02-01 17:33:39', '2014-02-01 16:33:39', '<!--:SR-->Tim koji radi na razvijanju vetroelektrane „Plandište 1“ čine stručnjaci različitih profila: inženjeri građevine, mašinstva, elektrotehnike i zaštite životne sredine, uz stručnu podršku poznatih srpskih i svetskih kuća specijalizovanih u oblastima energetike i obnovljivih izvora energije i drugih relevantnih oblasti.\r\n\r\nJak menadžment tim vodi ovaj projekat od samog starta i zaslužan je za reputaciju vetroelektrane „Plandište 1“ koja važi za najnapredniji objekat ove vrste u Srbiji i prvi energetski objekat za proizvodnju električne energije koji će biti priključena na prenosni elektroenergetski sistem Srbije posle više od dve decenije. Projekat poseduje sve građevinske dozvole potrebne za njegovu realizaciju.<!--:--><!--:en--><h1>Team</h1>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h5>The team working on the development of “Plandište 1“ wind park consists of experts of various profiles: civil, machine, electrical and environmental engineers, with the expert support of renowned Serbian and world companies specializing in energy and renewable energy sources and other relevant fields.\r\n\r\nA strong management team has been leading the project from the very beginning and is responsible for the reputation of the “Plandište 1” wind park as the most advanced facility of its type in Serbia and the first power facility for electric power production to be connected to the electricity transmission system in Serbia after more than two decades. The project disposes with all the building permits required for its implementation.</h5>\r\n</div><!--:-->', '<!--:SR-->Tim<!--:--><!--:en-->Team<!--:-->', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '24-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-02-01 17:33:39', '2014-02-01 16:33:39', '', 24, 'http://nemanja-pc/?p=77', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
